- **Speed:** Use Canvas for all long-form content (faster iteration than chat). Work section-by-section. Use editing tools instead of regenerating.
- **Quality:** Better prompts = less editing. Invest 5 minutes in prompt specificity to save 20 minutes of editing.
- **Cost:** GPT-5 included in ChatGPT Plus ($20/month). If creating 15-20 pieces per month, cost per piece = $1-1.50 (vs. $500-800 outsourcing).

